Opens a preview in a browser, updated upon buffer save. Same preview window is valid accross multiple mardown buffers.
It's a minor mode that makes use of [MarkdownMode markdown-mode.el], which can transform markdown into html and [[https://github.com/ahyatt/emacs-websocket websocket.el]] to deliver html to browser.

[https://github.com/ancane/markdown-preview-mode https://github.com/ancane/markdown-preview-mode]

*M-x markdown-preview-mode*
